  sodium: 700 mg
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/beef-tenderloin-and-balsamic-tomatoes-606cb02129d6895658330c18
